## ğŸ§® All-In & Side Pots

When players are all-in for different stack sizes:
- A **main pot** is created with the smallest all-in bet.
- Additional bets form **side pots** contested by remaining players.

**Resolution Order**:
1. Evaluate main pot first (all eligible players).
2. Then resolve side pots in order, comparing only hands of players still eligible.

Each pot may also be split across two boards.

